data.description: Final home for sale in prime Southern Hills community! Ready for move-in ranch home build by Richmond American. At the front of the home, you'll find two bedrooms flanking a full bath. Toward the back, there's a well-appointed kitchen nestled between an elegant dining room and generous great room. A tech center provides added convenience! The laundry is located near the owner's bedroom, which has a large walk-in closet and a private bath with double sinks. Features include a 2 car garage, maple cabinets, granite countertops, backsplash and stainless steel appliances in kitchen, tankless water heater, gas furnace, quartz countertops in bathrooms and more!  Community views of the Blue Ridge Mountains, directly off of I-81 and close to Old Town Winchester. Ask about warranty programs and closing cost assistance!
